quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  60,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  60,1,momino! agar tum meri raah mein larnay aur meri khushnodi talab karne ke liye ( mukkay se ) niklay ho to mere aur apne dushmanon ko dost nah banaao. tum to un ko dosti ke pegham bhaijtay ho aur woh ( deen ) haq se jo tumahray paas aaya hai munhkir hain. aur is baais se ke tum apne perwar-digaar khuda taala par imaan laaye ho paighambar ko aur tum ko jalaa-watan karte hain. tum un ki taraf posheeda posheeda dosti ke pegham bhaijtay ho. aur jo kuch tum makhfi tor par aur jo Ali al-elaan karte ho woh mujhe maloom hai. aur jo koi tum mein se aisa kere ga woh seedhay rastay se bhatak gaya
  60,2,agar yeh kafir tum par qudrat paleen to tumahray dushman ho jaien aur aeza ke liye tum par haath ( bhi ) chalayein aur zubanain ( bhi ) aur chahtay hain ke tum kisi terhan kafir hojao
  60,3,qayamat ke din nah tumahray rishte naatay kaam ayen ge aur nah aulaad. is roz wohi tum mein faisla kere ga. aur jo kuch tum karte ho khuda is ko daikhta hai
  60,4,tumhe ibrahim aur un ke رفقاء ki naik chaal chalni ( zaroor ) hai. jab unhon ne apni qoum ke logon se kaha ke hum tum se aur un ( buton ) se jin ko tum khuda ke siwa pujte ho be talluq hain ( aur ) tumahray ( mabodon ke kabhi ) qaail nahi ( ho saktay ) aur jab taq tum khuday-e wahid aur imaan nah lao hum mein tum mein hamesha khullam khula adawat aur dushmani rahay gi. haan ibrahim ne apne baap se yeh ( zaroor ) kaha ke mein aap ke liye mughfirat maanguu ga aur khuda ke samnay aap ke baray mein kisi cheez ka kuch ikhtiyar nahi rakhta. ae hamaray perwar-digaar tujh hi par hamara bharosa hai aur teri hi taraf hum rujoo karte hain aur tairay hi huzoor mein ( hamein ) lout kar aana hai
  60,5,ae hamaray perwar-digaar hum ko kafiroon ke haath se azaab nah dilana aur ae perwar-digaar hamaray hamein maaf farma. be shak to ghalib hikmat wala hai
  60,6,tum ( musalmanoon ) ko yani jo koi khuda ( ke samnay jaane ) aur roz akhirat ( ke anay ) ki umeed rakhta ho usay un logon ki naik chaal chalni ( zaroor ) hai. aur rogrdani kere to khuda bhi be parwah aur sazawar hamd (o sana ) hai
  60,7,ajab nahi ke khuda tum mein aur un logon mein jin se tum dushmani rakhtay ho dosti peda kardey. aur khuda Qadir hai aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  60,8,jin logon ne tum se deen ke baray mein jung nahi ki aur nah tum ko tumahray gharon se nikala un ke sath bhalai aur insaaf ka sulooq karne se khuda tum ko mana nahi karta. khuda to insaaf karne walon ko dost rakhta hai
  60,9,khuda un hi logon ke sath tum ko dosti karne se mana karta hai jinhon ne tum se deen ke baray mein larai ki aur tum ko tumahray gharon se nikala aur tumahray nikaalte mein ouron ki madad ki. to jo log aison se dosti karen ge wohi zalim hain
  60,10,momino! jab tumahray paas momin aurtain watan chore kar ayen to un ki azmaish karlo. ( aur ) khuda to un ke imaan ko khoob jaanta hai. so agar tum ko maloom ho ke momin hain to un ko kufar ke paas wapas nah bhaijho. ke nah yeh un ko halal hain aur nah woh un ko jaaiz. aur jo kuch unhon ne ( un par ) kharchkiya ho woh un ko day do. aur tum par kuch gunah nahi ke un aurton ko mohar day kar un se nikah karlo aur kafir aurton ki Namoos ko qabzay mein nah rakho ( yani kufar ko wapas day do ) aur jo kuch tum ne un par kharchkiya ho tum un se talab karlo aur jo kuch unhon ne ( apni aurton par ) kharchkiya ho woh tum se talab karlen. yeh khuda ka hukum hai jo tum mein faisla kiye deta hai aur khuda jan-nay wala hikmat wala hai
  60,11,aur agar tumhari aurton mein se koi aurat tumahray haath se nikal kar kafiroon ke paas chali jaye ( aur is ka mohar wusool nah howa ho ) phir tum un se jung karo ( aur un se tum ko ghanemat haath lagey ) to jin ki aurtain chali gayi hain un ko ( is maal mein se ) itna day do jitna unhon ne kharchkiya tha aur khuda se jis par tum imaan laaye ho daro
  60,12,ae paighambar! jab tumahray paas momin aurtain is baat par baet karne ko ayen ke khuda ke sath nah shirk karen gi nah chori karen gi nah badkaari karen gi nah apni aulaad ko qatal karen gi nah apne haath paon mein koi bohtan bandh layein gi aur nah naik kamon mein tumhari nafarmani karen gi to un se baet le lau aur un ke liye khuda se bakhshish mango. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  60,13,momino! un logon se jin par khuda ghusse howa hai dosti nah karo ( kyunkay ) jis terhan kafiroon ko mardon ( ke jee utney ) ki umeed nahi isi terhan un logon ko bhi akhirat ( ke anay ) ki umeed nahi
